history.content:
Hey everyone! 

We've created a website to help with the mental health problems that come from isolation and constant zoom as well as midterm anxiety.

The website is available at https://tinyurl.com/zoomhealth and I've also attached a flyer.

In addition, if you feel like you yourself have struggled and have a story to share on how you overcame your struggle, fill out this form and help others who may be feeling the same way currently! https://tinyurl.com/midtermtestimonials

Thank you!
history.subject: Zoom Mental Health Website
